"http://www.guardian.co.uk/")[標示出](http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/datablog/interactive/2011/aug/09/uk-
riots-incident-map?CMP=twt_fd
"http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/datablog/interactive/2011/aug/09/uk-riots-
incident-
map?CMP=twt_fd")全國經證實的騷亂地區，以及關鍵[事實和數字](http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/datablog/2011/aug/09/uk-
riots-data-figures "http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/datablog/2011/aug/09/uk-
riots-data-figures")，自由專欄記者Neal
Mann（@[fieldproducer](http://twitter.com/#%21/fieldproducer
"http://twitter.com/#!/fieldproducer")）在[推特](http://twitter.com/#%21/fieldproducer/riots
"http://twitter.com/#!/fieldproducer/riots")收集了駐倫敦採訪記者的名單。

